message.en_US: Spheromancer Lea! There you are!
message.pt_BR: Esferomante Lea! Aí está você!
message.de_DE: Spheromancer Lea! Du hast es also auch geschafft!
message.ja_JP:
スフィロマンサーのレア！
ようやく来たな！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: It looks like the Spheromancers are leading the race as of now!
message.pt_BR: Parece que os Esferomantes estão liderando a corrida a partir de agora!
message.de_DE: Damit führen die Spheromancer in diesem Rennen!
message.zh_CN: 看来比赛是气圆使者领先！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
今のところ、スフィロマンサーたちが
一歩リードしているようだな！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 看來比賽是氣圓使者領先！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Let's continue before that Pentafist catches up-
message.pt_BR: Vamos continuar antes que a Pentapunho nos alcance-
message.de_DE: Lass uns weitermachen, bevor dieser Pentafist uns einhol-
message.zh_CN: 我们最好在那个武星拳手来之...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
あのペンタフィストが
やってくる前に続きを―<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 저 오권사가 우릴 따라잡기 전에 어서 계속하-<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 我們最好在那個武星拳手來之...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Oh! Another shared outdoor area?
message.pt_BR: Ah! Outra área externa compartilhada?
message.de_DE: Oh! Noch ein uninstanzierter Außenbereich?
message.zh_CN: 哦？又一片共享户外区域！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
あれ？共有された
外部エリアかな？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 哦？又一片共享戶外區域！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: And I'm last, aren't I?
message.pt_BR: E eu sou a última, não é?
message.de_DE: Und ich bin Letzte, oder?<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP: 私が最後みたいだね？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

message.en_US: Indeed! We Spheromancers are at the very front, as expected!
message.pt_BR: Claro! Nós Esferomantes estamos na frente, como esperado!
message.de_DE: In der Tat! Wir Spheromancer stehen an vorderster Front - wie erwartet!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_CN: 没错！而第一名果不其然是我们气圆使者！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP:
その通り！我らスフィロマンサーたちが
予想通りリードしているのさ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_TW: 沒錯！而第一名果不其然是我們氣圓使者！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

message.en_US: Oui, oui, just keep your smug face while it lasts.
message.pt_BR: Oui, oui, comtinue se achando enquanto pode.
message.de_DE: Oui, oui, lach nur, so lang du noch kannst.
message.zh_CN: 啧啧，你就趁现在嚣张吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
message.ja_JP:
はいはい、今のうちに
そうやって得意げにしてなさいよ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
message.ko_KR: 그래, 그래. 잘난 척할 수 있을 때 많이 해둬.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
message.zh_TW: 嘖嘖，你就趁現在囂張吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]

message.en_US: The race isn't over yet!
message.pt_BR: A corrida ainda não terminou!
message.de_DE: Das Rennen ist noch nicht vorbei!
message.ja_JP:
レースはまだ
終わってないからね！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Spheromancer Lea! There you are!
message.pt_BR: Esferomante Lea! Aí está você!
message.de_DE: Spheromancer Lea! Da bist du ja!
message.ja_JP:
スフィロマンサーのレア！
ようやく来たな！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: I just got here myself. Grasshead has been waiting.
message.pt_BR: Eu acabei de chegar aqui. O Cabeça de grama estava esperando.
message.de_DE: Ich bin auch eben erst angekommen. Graskopf hat hier schon gewartet.
message.zh_CN: 我也刚到。绿草头比我们快。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
私も今着いたところだよ。
緑のツンツン頭は待ってたみたい。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 난 조금 전에 도착했어. 잡초 머리는 이미 기다리고 있었고.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 我也剛到。綠草頭比我們快。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Indeed.
message.pt_BR: Claro.
message.de_DE: In der Tat.
message.ja_JP: その通りだ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Still I'm saddened to see a Spheromancer overtaken by a mere Pentafist.
message.pt_BR: Ainda me entristece ver uma Esferomante ultrapassada por uma mera Pentapunho.
message.de_DE: Dennoch betrübt es mich zu sehen, dass ein Pentafist einen Spheromancer überholt.
message.zh_CN: 不过气圆使者竟然比不过武星拳手，实在令我失望。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
しかし、たかがペンタフィスト風情に
スフィロマンサーが遅れを取るとは、
俺は悲しいぞ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 원술사가 허접한 오권사보다 늦게 오다니 참 슬픈 일이군.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 不過氣圓使者竟然比不過武星拳手，實在令我失望。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Well, the race isn't over yet.
message.pt_BR: Bem, a corrida não acabou ainda.
message.de_DE: Tja, das Rennen ist noch nicht vorbei.
message.ja_JP:
まあ、レースは
まだ終わってないし。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 뭐, 시합은 아직 끝난 게 아니니까.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Who knows, maybe this Pentafist Scrub will end up overtaking you as well!
message.pt_BR: Quem sabe, talvez a gentalha Pentapunho acabe ultrapassando você também!
message.de_DE: Wer weiß, vielleicht überholt der Pentafist-Amateur am Ende auch dich!
message.zh_CN: 说不定最后胜利的会是你看不起的武星拳手呢！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
ひょっとしたら、
このペンタフィストの雑魚が
あなたも負かしちゃうかもよ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 누가 알아, 혹시 이 하찮은 오권사가 마지막엔 네 자리도 꿰찰지!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 說不定最後勝利的會是你看不起的武星拳手呢！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Anyway, we all just crossed blades with the Son of the East.
message.pt_BR: De qualquer forma, todos nós acabamos de duelar com o Filho do Oriente.
message.de_DE: Jedenfalls haben wir soeben alle die Klingen mit dem Sohn des Ostens gekreuzt.
message.zh_CN: 总之，我们刚刚都与东方之子交过手。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
ところで、みな東の御子とは
刃を交えたと思うのだが。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 아무튼, 우린 방금 동쪽의 아들과 격전을 벌였잖아.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 總之，我們剛剛都與東方之子交過手。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Still think it's just a funny ape, Pentafist?
message.pt_BR: Ainda acha que ele é apenas um macaco engraçado, Pentapunho?
message.de_DE: Glaubst du immer noch, er sei bloß ein lustiger Affe, Pentafist?
message.zh_CN: 还觉得那只是只蠢猴子吗，武星拳手？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
ペンタフィスト、お前はまだ
あれが面白いサルだと
思っているのか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 참 웃긴 유인원이라고 생각하지 않아, 오권사?<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 還覺得那只是只蠢猴子嗎，武星拳手？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: That battle was quite intense, non?
message.pt_BR: Aquela batalha foi bastante tensa, non?
message.de_DE: Der Kampf war recht fordernd, non?
message.ja_JP:
あのバトルは
かなり激しかったよね。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Apes are still funny, though! That will never change!
message.pt_BR: Apesar disso, macacos ainda são engraçados! Isso nunca vai mudar!
message.de_DE: Aber Affen sind trotzdem lustig! Und das wird auch immer so bleiben!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_CN: 不过猴子就是猴子，搞笑这点不会变！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP:
それでもサルは面白いよ！
それは変わらないもんね！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ko_KR: 하지만 유인원은 웃기긴 하지! 그 사실은 변하지 않아!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 不過猴子就是猴子，搞笑這點不會變！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

message.en_US: Now, let's race on!!
message.pt_BR: Agora, vamos continuar a corrida!
message.de_DE: Weiter geht's!!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP: よし、レース再開だ！！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

text.pt_BR: Eu te falei, né? Grande vista!
text.de_DE: Hab ich doch gesagt, oder? Großartige Aussicht!
text.ja_JP:
言ったでしょ、
すごい眺めだって！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_CN: 跟你说了吧，这里的景色超赞！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_TW: 跟你說了吧，這裡的景色超贊！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: You can barely see anything through the leaves...
text.pt_BR: Quase não se vê nada através das folhas...
text.de_DE: Durch die Blätter sieht man fast nix...
text.ja_JP:
木の葉でさえぎられて
ほとんどなにも見えないよ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: Come on, let's continue with the temple.
text.pt_BR: Qual é, vamos continuar com o templo.
text.de_DE: Ach, memm nich' rum, weiter geht's.
text.ja_JP:
ねえねえ、
早く神殿を進めようよ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_CN: 行了，我们继续打神庙吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_TW: 行了，我們繼續打神廟吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

message.en_US: Hi!
message.pt_BR: Oi!
message.de_DE: Hi!

message.en_US: Countless leaves.
message.pt_BR: Inúmeras folhas.
message.de_DE: Unzählige Blätter.
message.ja_JP: 数え切れないほどの葉っぱ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

message.en_US: Bundled together.
message.pt_BR: Agrupadas em conjunto.
message.de_DE: Zusammengebündelt.
message.ja_JP: いくつも束になってる。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

message.en_US: Like green clouds, up in the sky.
message.pt_BR: Como nuvens verdes, lá no céu.
message.de_DE: Wie grüne Wolken am Himmel.
message.ja_JP:
まるで空に浮かぶ
緑の雲のように。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
message.ko_KR: 마치 하늘 위에 있는 초록색 구름 같도다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

message.en_US: [nods]
message.pt_BR: [acena a cabeça]
message.de_DE: [nickt]
message.ja_JP: [うなずく]<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: There are...\. too many of them...\. and too little space...
text.pt_BR: Há..\. muitas delas...\. e muito pouco espaço...
text.de_DE: Da sind...\. zu viele von denen...\. auf viel zu engem Raum...
text.ja_JP:
あいつらが...\.あいつらが
あんなにたくさん...\.
それもせまい場所に...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.ko_KR: 녀석들이...\. 너무 많아...\. 공간은 너무 작은데...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: Don't give up, pal! I know you can do it!
text.pt_BR: Não desista, cara! Eu sei que você pode fazer isso!
text.de_DE: Nicht aufgeben, ich glaub' an dich!
text.ja_JP:
あきらめるな！
君ならできる！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.ko_KR: 포기하지 마, 친구! 넌 할 수 있어!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_CN: 别放弃！我知道你能做到的！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_TW: 別放棄！我知道你能做到的！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: And once I thought they were cute...
text.pt_BR: E antes eu achava eles bonitinhos...
text.de_DE: Und ich dachte mal, die wären süß...!
text.ja_JP:
一度かわいいなって
思っちゃうと...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_CN: 我还以为它们挺可爱的...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_TW: 我還以為它們挺可愛的...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: I knew it! Once I saw this giant tree, I knew this was gonna happen!
text.pt_BR: Eu sabia! Quando vi essa árvore gigante, sabia que isso ia acontecer!
text.de_DE: Ich wusste es! Als ich den großen Baum sah, da wusste ich, dass genau das passieren würde!
text.ja_JP:
だと思ってた！大きな木を
見たときからわかってた、
こうなるって！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.ko_KR: 이럴 줄 알았어! 이 거대한 나무를 봤을 때부터 이렇게 될 줄 알았다고!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_CN: 我就知道！我一看到巨树就知道会这样！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_TW: 我就知道！我一看到巨樹就知道會這樣！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: Of course they'd make us climb it up and walk on those narrow branches!!
text.pt_BR: Claro que eles nos fariam subir e caminhar sobre aqueles ramos estreitos!!
text.de_DE: Dass wir da hochklettern und über das dünne Geäst balancieren müssen!
text.ja_JP:
高いところまで登らせて、こんなに
細い枝の上を歩かせるなんて！
そうだろうと思った！！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.ko_KR: 이 나무에 올라 얇은 가지 위를 걷게 하려고 했겠지!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_CN: 他们肯定要让我们爬这些细枝！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_TW: 他們肯定要讓我們爬這些細枝！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

text.en_US: Those stupid game designers with their stupid heights!!
text.pt_BR: Esses estúpidos designers de jogos com suas estúpidas alturas!!
text.de_DE: Diese bekloppten Spieledesigner mit ihren dämlichen Höhen!!
text.ja_JP:
バカげた高さまで登らせるなんて、
ゲームデザイナーたちは
バカなんじゃないの！！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.ko_KR: 바보 같은 게임 디자이너에 바보 같은 높이야!!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_CN: 那些关卡设计师肯定都是恶鬼！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
text.zh_TW: 那些關卡設計師肯定都是魔鬼！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

message.en_US: Really now...
message.pt_BR: Sério...
message.de_DE: Jetzt mal im Ernst...

message.en_US: A laughing monkey flying on a cloud?
message.pt_BR: Um macaco engraçado voando sobre uma nuvem?
message.ja_JP:
雲に乗って飛び回る、
笑うサルとはね。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Ein lachender Affe, der auf einer Wolke fliegt?

message.en_US: This is ridiculous, don't you agree?
message.pt_BR: Isso é ridículo, você não concorda?
message.ja_JP:
バカバカしいったら。
そう思わないか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Das ist doch albern, oder nicht?

message.en_US: [nods]
message.pt_BR: [acena a cabeça]
message.ja_JP: [うなずく]<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: [nickt]

message.en_US: Right? What were developers thinking!
message.pt_BR: Não é? O que os desenvolvedores tinham na cabeça!
message.zh_CN: 对吧，开发者在想什么呢！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 그렇지? 대체 개발자들은 무슨 생각을 하는 건지!<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
だよな？開発者は
なにを考えてるんだ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Ja, eben! Was haben sich die Entwickler nur dabei gedacht?
message.zh_TW: 對吧，開發者在想什麼呢！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: [shakes head]
message.pt_BR: [balança a cabeça]
message.ja_JP: [首を振る]<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: [schüttelt Kopf]

message.en_US: Hmm, then it must be just me.
message.pt_BR: Hmm, então deve ser só eu.
message.zh_CN: 好吧，也许只是我有意见。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
うーん、じゃあ
俺がおかしいだけか。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Hmm... Dann sehe ich das wohl nur so.
message.zh_TW: 好吧，也許只是我有意見。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: Honestly, these boss fights are getting a tiny bit too crazy for my taste.
message.pt_BR: Honestamente, essas lutas de chefões estão ficando um pouco loucas demais para o meu gosto.
message.zh_CN: 这些boss照我看有些设计的太过了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 솔직히 말하자면 나한테 조금 정신없는 보스 전투 같아.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
正直言うと、俺の好みから見てだけど、
ボス戦がだんだん、ちょっとずつ
おかしくなってると思うんだよな。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Ehrlich gesagt werden diese Bosskämpfe langsam ein bisschen zu verrückt für meinen Geschmack.
message.zh_TW: 這些boss在我看來，有些設計的太過分了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: What next?\. Will the ape surf on a hover board or something?
message.pt_BR: O que vem a seguir?\. O macaco vai surfar em uma prancha ou algo assim?
message.zh_CN: 以后还会遇到啥?\.猩猩冲浪吗？<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.ko_KR: 이제 다음에 뭐지?\. 유인원이 호버보드라도 타는 건가?<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.ja_JP:
次はなんだ？\.ホバーボードかなんかで
サーフィンするサルでも出すか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.de_DE: Was kommt als Nächstes?\. Dass der Affe auf einem Hoverboard surft?
message.zh_TW: 以後還會遇到什麼?\.猴子滑滑板嗎？<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
